data.description: NO MONEY DOWN if you QUALIFY! MINI FARM in beautiful HOME with a Mountain View! Located on 3.98 acre, 3 bedroom/2 bath home features BONUS Sunroom with wood burning stove, large detached workshop, potting/storage shed, PLUS 2 barns! Beautifully updated DECOR and appliances throughout & MOVE in READY! Every room in this home is spacious! The 3rd Bedroom has been made into an office/work out area but could EASILY be converted back to 4 bedrooms if desired! The open concept kitchen/dining area is huge with built in's, pantry, island & more!  Electric Fireplace in Living area, HUGE master suite, walk in closet & updated bath! Ask for a complete list of updates and schedule your showing NOW!
